After many questions and phone calls Enhle decided to make a public statement. "So, I've been getting a lot of phone calls about my name change. My name doesn't change professionally, my name remains Enhle Mbali," she said. Enhle explained that her surname, however, had changed to Maphumulo. The actress added that she wanted to clear up any confusion that may have existed. Watch the full video here: A video posted by Enhle mbali Mlotshwa (@enhlembali_) on Jan 25, 2017 at 1:43am PST